main event: A witness observed a large, silent, bright light that appeared to change shape from round to triangular and then disappeared behind trees.
interesting points: The object was well-developed and observed for 19 minutes.
The object's course was from south to north.
The witness reported the sighting by telephone.
The report notes that the information was conflicting and put in the 'mailability tray'.
The conclusion was that the sighting was 'unknown'.
sighted object: a large, bright light that changed shape
